description: I keep hearing about all the overwhelmed hospitals. I drove by the 3 major ones in my area because of the #filmyourhospital trend. Empty. Quiet. The second picture is the front door of the testing tent. Locked! They didn’t even have a need to open it! I know people are sick. But, the mass hysteria is the real problem. #covid #qarmy #wwg1wga #qanon #corona
